OL,3,CMore than 140 jobs cut as Hotpoint
OL,4,Cfactory to close after Christmas
OL,6,FMore than 140 jobs will be lost when
OL,7,FHotpoint closes its factory in Yate at
OL,8,Fthe end of the year.
OL,10,FOwner Beko Europe says the South
OL,11,FGloucestershire site will shut on New
OL,12,FYear's Eve, after more than a century
OL,13,Fof manufacturing.
OL,15,FSpeaking in July as a consultation
OL,16,Fopened, the company said the facility
OL,17,Fon Station Road has been operating at
OL,18,F"a significant loss" due to "a
OL,19,Fdecrease in demand" for tumble driers.
